    <item>
      <title>韩国动乱冲击美国亚洲联盟</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-04/south-korean-turmoil-strikes-at-heart-of-us-alliances-in-asia</link>
      <description><![CDATA[韩国总统可能因试图实施戒严而遭到弹劾，这可能会破坏美国主导的东亚联盟，从而影响美国在当选总统唐纳德·特朗普领导下对中国加大施压的努力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-04/south-korean-turmoil-strikes-at-heart-of-us-alliances-in-asia</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 04 Dec 2024 11:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>唐纳德·特朗普和哈维尔·米莱为何在紧缩政策上分歧巨大</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-04/why-donald-trump-and-javier-milei-are-worlds-apart-on-austerity</link>
      <description><![CDATA[从发型、社交媒体和针对对手的策略来看，唐纳德·特朗普和阿根廷总统哈维尔·米莱伊似乎是一丘之貉。但风格和实质是两码事。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-04/why-donald-trump-and-javier-milei-are-worlds-apart-on-austerity</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 04 Dec 2024 11:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普誓言“扣押”国会拨款。他能做到吗？</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-04/impoundment-can-trump-refuse-to-spend-money-congress-appropriates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[当选总统唐纳德·特朗普表示，他有很多方法可以缩减联邦政府规模：取消教育部；授权两个富有的盟友成立一个非官方的政府效率部；削减监管政府的官僚机构。还有一个想法：不要把国会让他花的钱全部花掉。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-04/impoundment-can-trump-refuse-to-spend-money-congress-appropriates</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 04 Dec 2024 10:00:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧洲商业团体调查发现中国挑战日益严峻</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-04/european-business-groups-surveys-find-rising-china-challenges</link>
      <description><![CDATA[两项最新调查显示，英国和德国企业在中国开展业务的日子越来越难过，而且他们对明年的前景感到担忧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-04/european-business-groups-surveys-find-rising-china-challenges</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 04 Dec 2024 09:00:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
