    <item>
      <title>韩国央行行长李承晚表示，鉴于尹富比的惊人举动，降息的可能性不大</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-04/bok-chief-rhee-says-unlikely-to-cut-rates-on-political-turmoil</link>
      <description><![CDATA[韩国央行行长李昌镕表示，央行不太可能降息，他淡化了总统尹锡烈实施戒严令所引发的政治混乱对经济的影响。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-04/bok-chief-rhee-says-unlikely-to-cut-rates-on-political-turmoil</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 04 Dec 2024 08:37:23 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
